reviews.text: Dr Green and his staff are very friendly and caring. Dr Green takes the time to thoroughly explain your treatment plan as well as listen to any concerns you may have. Since going to East York Chiropractic my back and neck pain have been significantly reduced! Dr Green also won't tell you that he can "fix" a spine issue if it's something that he truly can't treat. I would highly recommend East York Chiropractic.

I've been to chiropractors all over the country, but I always look forward to the friendly face of Robin and the caring hands of Dr. Greene to get me back in alignment and back on track. I highly recommend East York Chiropractic.  You won't be disappointed!

Donnie Hoffman                  I have had a problem with my neck for many years. I have been to many Doctors with little to no avail.  That was until I went to see Dr. Green.  After a few weeks he changed my life if you are looking for a chiropractic practice please give Dr Green and his staff a visit .Also I'd like to thank Robin and Lynn for all all there help as well
